reviewText: Soldier is one of the worst movies I ever watched. Tequilla Sunrise is ok, but just strange. Executive decision is a good movie and I haven't watched the unlawful entry as yet. I would say I got a good value for what I paid which I think was $12.

reviewText: This has got to be one of the best 4 pack collections ive ever had the pleasure of owning.This is without question kurt russell at his best with action galore,especially Executive decision.This flick packs heat with top notch acting and explosive drama ,hold on tight while you heart skips a beatevery time beautiful Halle Berry is on the screen.If you have never seen this pic,dont waste time and orderthis discounted four pack.Tequila Sunrise also a good film.the other 2 movies i would also recommend.!!!!!Michael Rivera.
